Package: getarc
Title: An R Wrapper for the ArcGIS Rest API
Version: 0.0.0.9500
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matthew",
           family = "Whittle",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "matthewjwhittle@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: getarc is an R wrapper for th ArcGIS Rest API. The package provides access to all the open souce data hosted on Arc GIS servers. The package currently supports querying data on map servers and feature servers.
